data.title: Candidates standing in the General Election 2024
data.text:
Election of a Member of Parliament

The following is a statement as to the persons nominated for election as a member of parliament for the Normanton and Hemsworth constituency.

This is for the Election of a member of parliament, to take place on 4 July 2024.
